Patrick St. Esprit https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrick_St._Esprit 0 Patrick St. Esprit (born May 18, 1954) is an American character actor, best known for playing Romulus Thread in The Hunger Games: Catching Fire, Elliot Oswald in Sons of Anarchy and Robert Hicks in S.W.A.T..
